"LSF in the dispersion direction. This alignment will be constrained by pins (Pins C & D in
Figure 5). Therefore, to ensure that this constraint can be placed using standard machining,
a standard machine tolerance has been adopted in this degree of freedom: ¬±127 ¬µm (3œÉ).
